---
title: Easy Harissa Chorizo, Sweet Potato and Butter Bean Stew with Dill, Bell Pepper and Garlic Ciabatta Dippers
description: Ready in just 25 minutes, this Easy Harissa Chorizo, Sweet Potato and Butter Bean Stew is full of veg. Harissa is widely used in Middle Eastern and North African cuisine, containing dried chillies, star anise, cumin and coriander.
